Ran pylint on python file changes and fixed issues. There were still three notices on tensorflow/python/util/compat.py of:

tensorflow/python/util/compat.py:58:2: R1705: Unnecessary "elif" after "return" (no-else-return)
tensorflow/python/util/compat.py:80:2: R1705: Unnecessary "elif" after "return" (no-else-return)
tensorflow/python/util/compat.py:109:2: R1705: Unnecessary "else" after "return" (no-else-return)

I hadn't made changes to these lines in this PR so didn't change.

All my changes for compat.py, compat_test.py and readers.py are now fixed for linting
